<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"
xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word"
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>Adab Tenant Application Form</title>
<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>
<w:WordDocument>
<w:View>Print</w:View>
<w:Zoom>100</w:Zoom>
</w:WordDocument>
</xml><![endif]-->
<style>
@page { size: A4; margin: 2cm; }
body { font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; color: #1B2A4A; }
h1 { font-size: 18pt; color: #1B2A4A; border-bottom: 2pt solid #C9A227; padding-bottom: 4pt; }
h2 { font-size: 12pt; color: #C9A227; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 4pt; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 10pt; }
td { border: 1pt solid #1B2A4A; padding: 8pt; vertical-align: top; height: 28pt; }
td.label { background: #F8F6F1; font-weight: bold; width: 38%; }
p { margin: 0 0 8pt; }
.note { font-size: 9pt; color: #6B7280; font-style: italic; }
.sig-line { border-bottom: 1pt solid #1B2A4A; height: 24pt; margin-top: 8pt; }
.footer { margin-top: 20pt; font-size: 9pt; color: #6B7280; text-align: center; border-top: 1pt solid #C9A227; padding-top: 8pt; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Tenant Application Form</h1>
<p><strong>Adab Real Estate Agency</strong> · Property: [Address / Listing ref]</p>
<p class="note">All information is confidential. Rent amounts in Nigerian Naira (NGN). Diaspora applicants may include overseas contact details.</p>

<h2>Applicant Details</h2>
<table>
<tr><td class="label">Full name</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Date of birth</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Nationality</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Phone (Nigeria)</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">WhatsApp number</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Email address</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Current address</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">NIN / ID type &amp; number</td><td></td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Employment &amp; Income</h2>
<table>
<tr><td class="label">Employer / Business name</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Job title</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Employer address</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Monthly income (NGN)</td><td>₦</td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Length of employment</td><td></td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Rental Requirements</h2>
<table>
<tr><td class="label">Desired move-in date</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Proposed rent (NGN/month)</td><td>₦</td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Number of occupants</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Pets</td><td>☐ Yes &nbsp; ☐ No — Details:</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>References</h2>
<table>
<tr><td class="label">Previous landlord name &amp; phone</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Personal reference (name &amp; phone)</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td class="label">Emergency contact</td><td></td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Declaration</h2>
<p>I confirm that the information provided is true and complete. I authorise Adab Real Estate Agency to verify details with references and conduct reasonable checks.</p>
<p>Applicant signature: <span class="sig-line">&nbsp;</span> &nbsp; Date: <span class="sig-line">&nbsp;</span></p>

<div class="footer">
Adab Real Estate Agency · hello@adab.ng · +234 812 827 2287 · adab.ng · CAC Reg. No. RC 9590252
</div>

</body>
</html>
